{"tid":2182443,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【小白求助】預算8k內可以打機嘅laptop","createTime":"2020-08-31T09:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T19:08:33.000Z","uid":373227,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"117f691c2a78b6d711098226e461b217030abeae","tid":2182443,"uid":373227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小妹今年做咗太空人，想係預算8k內買部laptop<br />\nClick入notebook ownership programme𥄫完先發現自己係咩都唔識睇嘅小薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />於是斗膽開post求各路大神打救小妹<br />\n<br />\n本身讀文學/人類學所以都係正常文書處理工作<br />\n然而我手痕想打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想玩apex呀跑呀之類<br />\n有時仲想玩下mmd 不過唔會玩到建模<br />\n<br />\n手持notebook ownership programme（moss)但係睇其他po話嗰啲機平係因為用cheap硬件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怕好易壞甚至終國的會爆炸<br />\n跪地問鼂咁多位大佬有冇推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感激不盡"},{"pid":"e9cd0aaea82fde22c483fb8959268d232ffb1aec","tid":2182443,"uid":52068,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"我想請問你&ldquo;小白&rdquo;係乜野意思？"},{"pid":"16e54c1e71c3a9be2a09c5912b32c6da391be400","tid":2182443,"uid":373227,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"e9cd0aaea82fde22c483fb8959268d232ffb1aec","tid":2182443,"uid":52068,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"我想請問你&ldquo;小白&rdquo;係乜野意思？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"Wow有時見台灣人都有講下仲以為用得 search咗先知原來係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住大佬 絕對冇下次"},{"pid":"3979b67d9f8eea163f76f9a44266019b3925943b","tid":2182443,"uid":373227,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"摸索咗好耐先搵到點回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁多位大佬原諒我啦<br />\n其實睇過一部Dell Inspiron 7501  7千零蚊好似唔錯但係見其他po話dell唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />spec如下<img src=\"https://