n你新移民嘅標準到底係乜撚嘢 健康都未出你已經幫人分撚咗級？咩都唔知就話人新移民蝗蟲呢啲先最撚乞人憎囉on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6b26ca63478f9033e4df6b1e4f73dd237aae9a","tid":2182443,"uid":119080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:33:15.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正經想打機建議Desktop 性能好散熱更加好 <br />\nlaptop打到機 但散熱唔好好易令性能降低 = 哂多左錢<br />\n<br />\n建議你平平地買部文書機上到堂<br />\n其他錢砌desktop"},{"pid":"30cbcb392d03f8c37cc906fd1279cd0caf7e31c7","tid":2182443,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d3246b540007072b391e0c504ed9499c6c6b6cfc","tid":2182443,"uid":338185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf2f70db9a39f87aadac23fa09038658c25c3a79","tid":2182443,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6731916d4666a302c74ecc5fde9982f3cd5ecc21","tid":2182443,"uid":338185,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"我係台灣咁耐都冇聽過有人叫自己小白<br />\n除左貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新手下話？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"有隻狗叫小白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"我隻貓叫小白"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"我個fd叫小白<br />\n<br />\n但佢唔白又唔係姓白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d334be0abcb7edbeba34030da79e09c5f749760a","tid":2182443,"uid":338185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea6b26ca63478f9033e4df6b1e4f73dd237aae9a","tid":2182443,"uid":119080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:33:15.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正經想打機建議Desktop 性能好散熱更加好 <br />\nlaptop打到機 但散熱唔好好易令性能降低 = 哂多左錢<br />\n<br />\n建議你平平地買部文書機上到堂<br />\n其他錢砌desktop"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗<br />\nDesktop㩒用好多啦 laptop頂多4-5年就唔掂<br />\nlaptop一黎散熱差 好鬼熱 辣到手痛（試過）<br />\n二黎8000嘅laptop性能同10000 desktop差好遠<br />\n仲有 laptop keyboard好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議砌desktop打機 然後買iPad/平嘅文書機返學<br />\nIpad嘅話輕便 可以買Logitech keyboard接住黎用<br />\n而家買好似送無線耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3fe817a4d9589d960117ff32280d36417eca90","tid":2182443,"uid":362459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"過來人 買平既LAPTOP打機 不如唔好買 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果部係ASUS TUF"},{"pid":"e6e1effffbd9e2bda1a441675b9926020c33c917","tid":2182443,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"自已搵集運送黎HK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/-/zh_TW/dp/B08842D7JS/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F-%2Fzh_TW%2Fdp%2FB08842D7JS%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=a3b74d0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/-/zh_TW/dp/B08842D7JS/</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"16e54c1e71c3a9be2a09c5912b32c6da391be400","tid":2182443,"uid":373227,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"Wow有時見台灣人都有講下仲以為用得 search咗先知原來係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住大佬 絕對冇下次"}}